### Describe the bug

The input code below, visit function accesses variable depth, however after minified, the depth becomes 0 when visit gets invoked

### Input code

```typescript
let depth = 0;

function foo(n) {
  depth += 1;
  let k = visit(n);
  depth -= 1;
  return k;
}

blackbox(foo)
```


